#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/assigning_a_material.rst:69
msgid "Naming materials"
msgstr "命名材质"

#: ../../manual/render/blender_render/materials/assigning_a_material.rst:71
msgid ""
"It is a very good idea to give your materials clear names so you can keep"
" track of them, especially when they are linked to multiple objects. Try "
"to make your names descriptive of the material, not its function (e.g. "
"\"Yellow Painted\" rather than \"Kitchen Table Color\")."
msgstr "赋予材质一个明确的名字是个好办法，可以保持材质的可追踪性，特别是当材质与多个物体关联时。尽量使用描述性的材质名称，而不是其功能(如：\"黄色油漆\"，而不是\"厨房桌子颜色\")。"

